# ============================================================
# LIFE PLANNER APPLICATION ARCHITECTURE
# ============================================================

actors:
  - owner
  - family_viewer
  - family_editor

main_modules:
  - plan management
  - timeline management
  - goal management
  - review log management
  - family sharing management
  - scenario comparison
  - reflection candidate intake

architecture_rules:
  - ownerが最終確定権限を持つ
  - family_editorは編集可能だが自動確定不可
  - family_viewerは閲覧のみ
  - 他アプリ情報は反映候補として保持する
